about.summary: A set of handy functions. Includes a versatile one line progress bar, one  line function timer with detailed output, time delay function, text histogram, object  preview, CRAN package search, simpler package installer, Linux command install check,  a flexible Mode function, top function, simulation of correlated data, and more.

name: r-ncmisc
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set version = '1.1.6' %}
{% set posix = 'm2-' if win else '' %}
{% set native = 'm2w64-' if win else '' %}

package:
  name: r-ncmisc
  version: {{ version|replace("-", "_") }}

source:
  url:
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/NCmisc_{{ version }}.tar.gz
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/Archive/NCmisc/NCmisc_{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 2aa85997d5ec2222e610604022684c004a4925241761d9a0104919f1cf3a8c79

build:
  merge_build_host: True  # [win]
  number: 1
  noarch: generic
  rpaths:
    - lib/R/lib/
    - lib/

requirements:
  build:
    - {{ posix }}zip               # [win]
  host:
    - r-base
    - r-proftools
  run:
    - r-base
    - r-proftools

test:
  commands:
    - $R -e "library('NCmisc')"           # [not win]
    - "\"%R%\" -e \"library('NCmisc')\""  # [win]

about:
  home: https://CRAN.R-project.org/package=NCmisc
  license: GPL (>= 2)
  summary: A set of handy functions. Includes a versatile one line progress bar, one  line function
    timer with detailed output, time delay function, text histogram, object  preview,
    CRAN package search, simpler package installer, Linux command install check,  a
    flexible Mode function, top function, simulation of correlated data, and more.
  license_family: GPL3
  license_file: '{{ environ["PREFIX"] }}/lib/R/share/licenses/GPL-2'

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - conda-forge/r
